nodes.text: The Dreamer and the Dreamt were the mysterious pair known as the Sheelal in Kaleesh, whose fates were intertwined over eternity.

After a strange dream was had by Kaleesh warlord Qymaen jai Sheelal, and the sudden appearance of Ronderu lij Kummar, Qymaen was considered to be the living manifestation of the Dreamer, and Ronderu, the Dreamt.
